Cell["\<\
The MOT coils will be wound from 1/4\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] circular copper \
tubing with insulation. This is stock from McMaster-Carr \
(https://www.mcmaster.com/3041K11) \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8024843358936768`*^9, 3.80248441475384*^9}, {
  3.802484681912467*^9, 3.802484692369644*^9}, {3.80248472927033*^9, 
